sequenceDiagram
  participant Source
  participant Kafka
  participant Bronze
  participant Silver
  participant Gold
  participant Warehouse
  participant AI
  participant Audit
  Source->>Kafka: transaction and fraud events
  Kafka->>Bronze: raw payload append with checkpoint
  Bronze->>Silver: schema validation, dedupe, masking
  Silver->>Gold: KPI aggregation and quality scoring
  Gold->>Warehouse: executive marts
  Gold->>AI: approved context indexing
  AI->>Audit: cited answer audit event
  Warehouse->>Audit: report validation event

